<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The CH combination is one of the most productive digraphs in English — appearing in hundreds of valid Scrabble words across every position. Whether you are starting a word with CHAMP, threading through with ANCHOR, or finishing with RICH, knowing your CH words gives you flexible scoring options on almost any board state.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why CH Is a Power Combination</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
